# Zen-Brain Home Directory

This directory is created by zen-brain on first run.

## Structure

- `journal/` - ZenJournal event logs (immutable)
- `context/` - Session state and work memory
- `cache/` - Ephemeral data (safe to delete)
- `config/` - Configuration files
- `logs/` - Application logs

## Build Artifacts (do not commit)

bin/
coverage.out
